description:
Eduard Strauss Huldigungen, Walzer, op. 88

Eduard Strauss Huldigungen, Walzer, op. 88 was first published in Vienna in 1885 by the publisher Spina. In the same year, 1885, the Sultan of the Ottoman Empire Abdul-Aziz-Khan, on a visit to Vienna, Eduard Strauss dedicates to him this waltz and he receives his highest award.

Pavel Kogan, Moscow State Symphony Orchestra, 2015.
